               </p>
               <p>"was in custody. He said, Mr. Dean, his</p>
               <p>"lawyer, was there, but that whether he was</p>
               <p>"taken into custody, or whether he surrendered</p>
               <p>"himself, he knew nothing at all</p>
               <p>"about it."</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17750531-2-person244">
