                  </persName>
            . I am a scrivenor, opposite the Admiralty. I filled up the bond that is now produced; it is my hand-writing. The prisoner and his brother were with me together, and have filled up bonds signed, 
               <persName id="t17750531-2-person245">
                  William
                   Adair
               <interp inst="t17750531-2-person245" type="surname" value="Adair"></interp>
