                  </persName>
            ; but which of the brothers gave me instructions to fill them up I cannot possibly tell; but I never did fill up a bond of Mr. 
               <persName id="t17750531-2-person246">
                  William
                   Adair
               <interp inst="t17750531-2-person246" type="surname" value="Adair"></interp>
